1. *Pokušava* da napravi svoje posao koliko je bolje moguće. (He is trying to do his job as best as he can.)
2. Ona se *pokušava* da se oporavi od teške bolesti. (She is trying to recover from a serious illness.)
3. On *pokušavao* je da se izbori sa problemima. (He was trying to cope with the problems.)
4. Ona *pokušavala* je da nađe rešenje za njihov problem. (She was trying to find a solution to their problem.)
5. Oni se *pokušavaju* da pronađu odgovor. (They are trying to find an answer.)